---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — xSoft Ltd | How We Protect Your Data" description="Privacy policy for xSoft Ltd and all services operated under xSoft. GDPR compliant. We collect minimal data and never sell your information." keywords="privacy policy, xSoft, GDPR, data protection">

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    "name": "Privacy Policy",
    "url": "https://www.xsoftlimited.com/privacy/",
    "description": "Privacy policy for xSoft Ltd. GDPR compliant.",
    "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "xSoft Ltd", "url": "https://www.xsoftlimited.com" },
    "dateModified": "2026-07-15"
  })} />

  <section class="pt-10 pb-8 border-b border-gray-800/50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="animate-fade-in-up text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="animate-fade-in-delay-1 mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Last updated: 15 July 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">Who We Are</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">xSoft Ltd (Company No. 17308915) is a private limited company registered in England & Wales. We operate several websites including xsoftlimited.com, scrabblewordsfinder.com, xconvert24.com, and xcrypto24.com.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-3">Contact: <a href="mailto:info@xsoftlimited.com" class="text-indigo-400 hover:underline">info@xsoftlimited.com</a></p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">What Data We Collect</h2>
      <div class="my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
          <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">Contact Form Submissions</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Name, email address, and message content — only when you voluntarily submit a form.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
          <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">Anonymous Usage Data</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Page visits, click interactions, country (from IP), device type, and browser. No personal identification.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
          <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">Technical Data</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">IP address (for security and anti-abuse), browser type, screen resolution. Stored anonymously.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">What We Don't Collect</h2>
      <div class="my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-red-500/30 bg-red-950/10">
          <p class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-sm">✗ No personal accounts</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-red-500/30 bg-red-950/10">
          <p class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-sm">✗ No payment information</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-red-500/30 bg-red-950/10">
          <p class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-sm">✗ No tracking across sites</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-red-500/30 bg-red-950/10">
          <p class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-sm">✗ No data sold to third parties</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">How We Use Data</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">We use collected data to:</p>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-300">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> Respond to your enquiries</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> Improve our websites and services</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> Monitor site health and performance</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> Prevent abuse and protect security</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">Data Storage & Security</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Data is stored on Cloudflare's infrastructure (D1 databases, KV stores) distributed globally with encryption at rest and in transit. We do not transfer data outside of Cloudflare's network.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Our sites use minimal cookies — primarily for admin authentication sessions. We do not use third-party advertising cookies or cross-site tracking pixels.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Under UK GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-300">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> Access any personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> Object to processing of your data</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span> Request a copy of your data in a portable format</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-3">To exercise any of these rights, email <a href="mailto:info@xsoftlimited.com" class="text-indigo-400 hover:underline">info@xsoftlimited.com</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
